channel.title: Rune-MTP 634 v2 - 2 new random pics
channel.description:
I now host this 24/7 btw with webclient.
[b]YOU DON'T HAVE TO JUST VIEW, YOU CAN COMMENT TOO OMG![/b]
I'm sure some of you may remember my development of this a couple months ago. I did in fact host a version of this several months ago. It was based around the GE and you could just spawn all your items. There was no point to the server, which is one of the reasons while I quit it (I was also getting ddosed daily). I quit it mainly to develop it more but I worked on my 317 a lot more. I continued development of this and have some new features to share.
[b]Colors don't mean shit :P[/b]
[b]Features Recently Added:[/b] Npc Combat Npc Drops Clan Chat and PMing Wilderness Ditch for Edge Pking Korasi (Gotta love that Spec :P) Shops Trading Pro PVP Combat - really took a lot of work. Custom Title system - Unfortunately I saw something similar to mine was released recently. I see that theirs is that everyone has the same title. I can give whoever I want whatever title I want using a command.
There has been so much fixed, like dupes, bugs, etc.
I'm not the best video maker but i'm going to do some to show the features of the server. [b]NEX VID[/b]: WILL BE UPDATED BECAUSE SOMEONE RELEASED 100% RS NEX WHICH KICKS THE ASS OUT OF THE SHITTY NEX I MADE.
